ZH: 我找不到遥控器了。
EN: I can't find the remote control.

ZH: 你能把遥控器递给我吗？
EN: Can you pass me the remote control?

ZH: 我的遥控器没电了，你有充电器吗？
EN: My remote control is out of battery, do you have a charger?

ZH: 别动我的遥控器，我正在使用它。
EN: Don't touch my remote control, I'm using it.

ZH: 遥控器在哪里？我想换频道。
EN: Where is the remote control? I want to change the channel.

ZH: 哇，这个遥控器有很多按钮！
EN: Wow, this remote control has so many buttons!

ZH: 这个遥控器设计得很方便，用起来很顺手。
EN: This remote control is designed very conveniently, it's easy to use.

ZH: 这个遥控器的连接范围很广。
EN: This remote control has a wide range of connectivity.

ZH: 这个电视遥控器需要配对才能使用。
EN: This TV remote control needs to be paired before using.

ZH: 我的遥控器被宠物咬坏了，我需要修理它。
EN: My remote control was chewed by my pet, I need to repair it.

ZH: 这个遥控器的音量调节功能很灵敏。
EN: The volume adjustment function of this remote control is very sensitive.

ZH: 遥控器上的按钮有点卡，可能是灰尘太多了。
EN: The buttons on the remote control are a bit sticky, there might be too much dust.

ZH: 遥控器的背面有个拨码开关，你知道它的作用吗？
EN: There is a dip switch on the back of the remote control, do you know what it is for?

ZH: 这款遥控器可以控制多种家用电器。
EN: This remote control can control multiple household appliances.

ZH: 遥控器不起作用了，也许是电池放反了。
EN: The remote control is not working, maybe the batteries are put in the wrong way.

ZH: 我希望有个可以找回遥控器的功能，这样就不会经常丢了。
EN: I wish there was a feature that can help me find the remote control, so I won't lose it all the time.

ZH: 我把遥控器放在沙发下面了，你能帮我拿一下吗？
EN: I put the remote control under the sofa, can you help me get it?

ZH: 如果你不小心把遥控器打碎了，我可以帮你修理。
EN: If you accidentally break the remote control, I can help you repair it.

ZH: 这个遥控器有个自动关机的功能，省电又方便。
EN: This remote control has an automatic power-off feature, it's energy-saving and convenient.

ZH: 别忘了把遥控器放回原位，别弄丢了。
EN: Don't forget to put the remote control back where it belongs, don't lose it.
